## Troubleshooting

Here are some common issues in BrewMaster and their solutions.

-   ***Inventory Not Updating***  
    Ensure you have saved changes and try refreshing the app. 🔄
    
-   ***Delayed Order Notifications***  
    Check your internet connection and notification settings 📶.
    
-   ***Employee Shifts Overlapping***  
    Adjust the shift schedule to avoid overlap. 🛠️
    

